842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T21:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c1803b11e08f6b4c429bd6a23f23ca5d11c9d6","tid":308744,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T21:35:36.000Z","msg":"曾經在你手上的<br />\n那綻開的花<br />\n而你卻任它流走<br />\n在指間之中<br />\n這是何等殘酷的感性"},{"pid":"1ad8a16087bfdd815962091d542c666d211cdd95","tid":308744,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T21:36:25.000Z","msg":"曾經在你手上的<br />\n那綻開的花<br />\n而你卻任它流走<br />\n在指間之中<br />\n這是何等殘酷的感性"},{"pid":"506a838903c0d73a5e3ab8a53f13561ade239687","tid":308744,"uid":33041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T00:13:53.000Z","msg":"請問出處係咪都係顧城 我搵唔到<br />\n得第一首知道係避免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdccc4fdea5f2ff0f2a35d6e8f74ad6facffe71","tid":308744,"uid":127216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:31:45.000Z","msg":"淨係識顧城個首詩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曾經我都好認同首詩既意境<br />\n唔敢付出 成日驚失敗<br />\n但而家諗番轉頭<br />\n花開花落係自然既事<br />\n有過燦爛既一刻 總好過乜事都冇發生<br />\n亦好過眼白白睇住男神同第二個一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849ab4bbaa20f0023b7e40577c30d70099cb605e","tid":308744,"uid":123907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:20:33.000Z","msg":"你命中注定和風一樣<br />\n飄飄蕩蕩<br />\n在雲中遊戲<br />\n我曾幻想與你為伴<br />\n可應該有怎樣的家園<br />\n才能容納你<br />\n牆壁會令你窒息<br />\n你只能是風，而風<br />\n從不告訴我<br />\n何時何時來又何時去<br />\n風來我睜不開眼睛<br />\n風去塵埃遍地"},{"pid":"fe898122ed59233dee97e162ae85ccbb6cec09f5","tid":308744,"uid":88386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b902f12d5ccc17db70362e192f8d3e123de52fb","tid":308744,"uid":81751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:33:09.000Z","msg":"只是我彷彿再也起不來了 <br />\n彷彿我真的只是燈芯<br />\n燒到只剩餘燼<br />\n他經過我的時候靜靜的<br />\n什麼都沒有說<br />\n彷彿一切痛苦<br />\n都只是我給自己的幻象"},{"pid":"ac1835f10c81a6932692889047977e3d2c4113c6","tid":308744,"uid":18072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a1dd5ca8b5f434c9dc935dd26399590e271a7c","tid":308744,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T21:18:14.000Z","msg":"或許我所有的全世界<br />\n是通往你眼裡的單程車票<br />\n穿過你的山頂<br />\n越過你的湖泊<br />\n在那留下一足印記<br />\n你眼中的全世界<br />\n其實從不在乎那一廂情願的卑微吧"},{"pid":"3955dd31c5df47c81e8615ae90fb93f7097414ad","tid":308744,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T21:19:25.000Z","msg":"發明家把錯綜複雜的結構<br />\n朝天空堆放<br />\n稱其為建築<br />\n進入<br />\n並發明了城市<br />\n　<br />\n人魚的特長是喝水<br />\n每多喝一口<br />\n便更溺陷深淵<br />\n越靠近海床<br />\n便越重<br />\n越快樂"},{"pid":"d663abf2cf86dc44cf7934346d2afa0bfb92a6c0","tid":308744,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T16:49:18.000Z","msg":"致仲夏<br />\n如嘆息般短促<br />\n如囈語般夢幻<br />\n如花火般奪目<br />\n那個你從來不是你<br />\n在記憶中的那個你"},{"pid":"e9bba21e9e3a0d11f83c6f76e2e0f2d7a9ab087f","tid":308744,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T19:37:04.000Z","msg":"生如夏花般絢爛<br />\n死如秋葉般靜美"},{"pid":"3e8fb08a796b64b657571a367169f2757010ba30","tid":308744,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"所有美好的都已美好過了<br />\n甚至夜夜來弔唁的蝶夢也冷了<br />\n是的，至少你還有虛無留存<br />\n你說。至少你己懂得什麼是什麼了<br />\n是的，沒有一種笑是鐵打的<br />\n甚至眼涙也不是......"},{"pid":"830c84a1dcc7630fdb0517cda88afa028cd41887","tid":308744,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ae79e49354282eb33403fdf963049fd86acb9a","tid":308744,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:02:10.000Z","msg":"放逐了自已去流浪<br />\n流浪流浪流浪<br />\n直至飛蛾般撲向那道光<br />\n原來這就是最終章"},{"pid":"df479613534363f8c4ebdfdcd8f91376006a03e2","tid":308744,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T06:00:37.000Z","msg":"你說<br />\n聽說喜歡夏天開的花<br />\n就會死在夏天<br />\n我的懵懵而知<br />\n大概是在那斜陽之後<br />\n而你那夏花仍佇立依然"}]}